<hr class="margin-top-double" />

<div class="row margin-top-double">
  <div class="col-sm-8">
    <h2>ESG Management Overview</h2>
    <p>The ESG Management Assessment helps to evaluate how prepared a company is to manage ESG risks effectively, based on the extent to which relevant policies, programmes and management systems are in place.</p>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="row margin-top-double">
  <div class="col-sm-6">
    <table class="table">
      <thead>
        <th>Theme</th>
        <th class="col-sm-3 text-center">Score</th>
        <th class="col-sm-3 text-center">Benchmark</th>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        {{#each categoryBenchmarks}}
        <tr>
          <td><i class="fa fa-circle text-{{ @key }}"></i>&nbsp; {{indicatorTypeName @key}}</td>
          <td class="text-center">{{lookup ../categoryScores @key }}</td>
          <td class="text-center">{{lookup ../categoryBenchmarks @key }}</td>
        </tr>
        {{/each}}
      </tbody>
    </table>
  </div>
  <div class="col-sm-3 text-center">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-xs-11 col-xs-offset-1">
        <div class="ratings margin-top-double">
          <div class="right">
            <div class="pull-left label-small">0</div>
            <div class="pull-right label-small">10</div>

            <div class="clearfix">&nbsp;</div>

            <div class="bars management">
              {{#each categoryBenchmarks}}
                <div class="progress progress-xs transparent esg {{ @key }}">
                  <div class="progress-bar progress-bar-{{indicatorTypeName @key 'lower'}}" role="progressbar" aria-valuenow="{{math (lookup ../categoryScores @key) '*' 10 }}" aria-valuemin="0" aria-valuemax="100" style="width: {{math (lookup ../categoryScores @key) '*' 10 }}%">
                  <span class="sr-only">{{math (lookup ../categoryScores @key) '*' 10 }}</span>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="progress progress-xs transparent benchmark {{ @key }}">
                  <div class="progress-bar progress-bar-darkgray" role="progressbar" aria-valuenow="{{math (lookup ../categoryBenchmarks @key) '*' 10 }}" aria-valuemin="0" aria-valuemax="100" style="width: {{math (lookup ../categoryBenchmarks @key) '*' 10 }}%">
                  <span class="sr-only">{{math (lookup ../categoryBenchmarks @key) '*' 10 }}</span>
                  </div>
                </div>
              {{/each}}
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="clearfix">&nbsp;</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="col-sm-3 text-center">
    <h4 class="legend no-margin">Indicator Distribution</h4>
    <div id="indicator-distribution-chart"></div>
  </div>
</div>

{{#if score}}
<div class="row">
  <div class="col-sm-8">
    <a href="#" class="widget-toggle-link" data-target="assessment">
      <h2><i class="circle-icon ti-plus"></i>&nbsp; ESG Management Assessment</h2>
    </a>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="widget no-margin margin-bottom-double" data-id="assessment">
  <div class="widget-content" style="display:none;">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-sm-8">
        <p class="margin-bottom-double" style="padding-left:26px;">The assessment includes a mix of core and industry-specific indicators emphasising the main ESG issues facing an industry. The Peer Benchmark, developed from Sustainalytics research universe, represents the average performance of small and mid-cap public companies operating in the industry.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <table class="table">
      <thead>
        <th class="col-sm-3">
          Indicator
        </th>
        <th class="col-sm-1 text-center">
          Score
        </th>
        <th class="col-sm-1 text-center">
          <span class="popover-text" tabindex="0" role="button" data-toggle="popover" data-placement="right" data-trigger="focus" title="Benchmark Comparison" data-content="The benchmark provides an assessment of performance relative to mid-and-small cap public companies from Sustainalyticsâ€™ research universe. Users can view average performance at the indicator level for public companies operating in the same sub-sector or country.">
            Benchmark
          </span>
        </th>
        <th class="col-sm-3">
          Analysis
        </th>
        <th class="col-sm-3">
          Company Comments
        </th>
        <th class="col-sm-1">
          Documents
        </th>
      </thead>

      <tbody id="indicators-container">
      </tbody>
    </table>

  </div>
</div>
{{/if}}
